comments: Poole (WAS) lowers his hand down toward the ball and marginal brush contact occurs with Murray's (ATL) wrist at the end of the drive.
Poole (WAS) brings his hand toward the ball and marginal contact occurs with Bey's (ATL) left arm at the start of his drive.
Poole (WAS) lowers his arm down toward the ball and makes contact with Bey's (ATL) hand, pulling it off of the ball and the contact affects Bey's driving shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) is drawn into the air and comes down into Gafford's (WAS) space, making contact with his arm and body that impacts the shot attempt in the paint.
Avdija (WAS) places his hand on Young's (ATL) back while defending the inbound, the contact affects his SQBR.
Gafford (WAS) establishes himself in Bey's (ATL) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the screen.
Avdija (WAS) steps into Young's (ATL) path and is not in a legal guarding position when body contact occurs that affects Young's SQBR.
After the free throw attempt, Kuzma (WAS) interferes with the ball and prevents it from being promptly recovered by the official.
Bey (ATL) reaches in for the ball and initiates contact to Avdija's (WAS) shoulder after the gather, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Johnson (ATL) recovers the ball and lands on two feet. He then shuffles both feet before pivoting off of his left foot.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Capela (ATL) is the last to make contact with the ball prior to it falling out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to Washington.
Johnson (ATL) legally contests Kuzma's (WAS) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Johnson (ATL) inbounds the ball within five seconds of receiving it from the game official.
Bey (ATL) firms up in Avdija's (WAS) path and marginal contact occurs as the two players come together during the screen.
Coulibaly (WAS) extends his hand to Murray's (ATL) front and initiates contact that affects Murray's SQBR.
Bey (ATL) and Kuzma (WAS) come together at the same spot on the floor during the drive and Kuzma spins away from the marginal contact.
Avdija (WAS) turns his body into Young (ATL) and contact occurs that affects Young's SQBR.
Jones (WAS) commits a take foul on Johnson (ATL). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Capela (ATL) avoids making illegal contact with Kuzma (WAS) during his contest of Kuzma's driving dunk attempt.
Murray (ATL) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes one step before coming to a stop and establishing a pivot foot.
Avdija (WAS) commits a take foul on Murray (ATL). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Kuzma (WAS) grasps and promptly releases the front of Bey's (ATL) jersey as the ball comes off of the rim, and the contact during the rebounding opportunity is marginal.
